{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zz7psvosiudfugqnvakue6l","title":"Deref","desc":"","updated":1668871552511,"created":1668867656839,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.rust.Smart-Pointer.Deref","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"0b3d37f660420c6ab01bc13ad64086c8","links":[],"anchors":{"deref-trait---smart-pointer-as-reference":{"type":"header","text":"Deref trait - Smart pointer as reference","value":"deref-trait---smart-pointer-as-reference","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"intro":{"type":"header","text":"Intro","value":"intro","line":11,"column":0,"depth":2},"box-like-a-reference":{"type":"header","text":"Box Like a reference","value":"box-like-a-reference","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"define-a-smart-pointer":{"type":"header","text":"Define a smart pointer","value":"define-a-smart-pointer","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2},"implicit-deref-coercions":{"type":"header","text":"Implicit Deref Coercions","value":"implicit-deref-coercions","line":52,"column":0,"depth":2},"deref-coercion-with-mutability":{"type":"header","text":"Deref Coercion with Mutability","value":"deref-coercion-with-mutability","line":59,"column":0,"depth":2},"vocab":{"type":"header","text":"Vocab","value":"vocab","line":70,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"xpd7irdmeinvljufhfbgq6a","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"deref\">Deref<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#deref\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"deref-trait---smart-pointer-as-reference\">Deref trait - Smart pointer as reference<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#deref-trait---smart-pointer-as-reference\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/ch15-02-deref.html\">https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/ch15-02-deref.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"intro\">Intro<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#intro\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code>Deref</code> trait: customize the behavior of the dereference operatio <code>*</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"box-like-a-reference\">Box<t> Like a reference</t><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#box-like-a-reference\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-rust\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Box</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">new</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token macro property\">assert_eq!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// pass</span>\n    <span class=\"token macro property\">assert_eq!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// pass -> *y == 5 -> deref(y) = 5</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"define-a-smart-pointer\">Define a smart pointer<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#define-a-smart-pointer\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-rust\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">std<span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span>ops<span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Deref</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token type-definition class-name\">MyBox</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">impl</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MyBox</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">new</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">-></span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MyBox</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Mybox::new(T)</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">MyBox</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">impl</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Deref</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MyBox</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"token type-definition class-name\">Target</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// define an associated type for the Deref trait to use</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// borrows `self` -> returns a reference to the inner data</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">deref</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">-></span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">Self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Target</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// first value of the tuple struct</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// *y -> *(y.deref())</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// NOTE: returning the value directly would transfer the ownership of the innter value</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"implicit-deref-coercions\">Implicit Deref Coercions<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#implicit-deref-coercions\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Deref coercion</strong>: converts a reference to a type that implements the <code>Deref</code> trait into a reference to a reference to another type\n<ul>\n<li>force the <code>Deref</code> type to another reference type</li>\n<li><code>&#x26;String</code> -> <code>str</code> (String implements the <code>Deref</code> trait)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Rust automatically call the <code>defef()</code> function to convert the input type to the parameter type</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"deref-coercion-with-mutability\">Deref Coercion with Mutability<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#deref-coercion-with-mutability\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code>Deref</code>: override the <code>*</code> operator on immutable references</li>\n<li><code>DerefMut</code>: override the <code>*</code> operator on mutable references</li>\n<li>Rust does deref coercions when\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#x26;T</code> => <code>&#x26;U</code>: <code>T: Deref&#x3C;Target=U></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x26;mut T</code> => <code>&#x26;mut U</code>: <code>T: DerferMut&#x3C;Target=U></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x26;mut T</code> => <code>&#x26;U</code>: <code>T:Deref&#x3C;Target=U></code> </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Rust will also coerce a mutable reference to an immutable one</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"vocab\">Vocab<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#vocab\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>coercion <code>/kəʊˈɜː.ʃən//</code>: the practice of persuading someone to do something by using force or threats.\n<ul>\n<li>sự bắt buộc || sự cưỡng bách</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","v